        "subject": "LU-10973 lutf: stubs for APIs which use struct lnet_nid",
        "message": "LU-10973 lutf: stubs for APIs which use struct lnet_nid\n\nNeed to add stubs for APIs which use struct lnet_nid in user space,\nbecause the LUTF uses the .h file for swig wrapping. When the\ngenerated python module is imported into the python interpreter\nrunning inside the LUTF it complains about these functions being\nundefined.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\n\nSigned-off-by: Amir Shehata <ashehata@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Ieb41509a917e27c69632314c0270e9e640ca132b\n"
